        "content": "## Monitor spend with HTTP / REST API and Slack\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring\n**Trigger:** Scheduled\n**Integrations:** HTTP / REST API, Slack\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original FlowDex template.",
